act.article:
2 Definitions. In these rules, unless the context otherwise requires,
a Act' means the Armed Forces Tribunals Act, 2007 (55 of 2007);
b Chairperson means the Chairperson of the Tribunal;
c Tribunal means the Armed Forces Tribunal. ___________
1 Vide S.R.O. 25(E), dated 12th September, 2008, published in the Gazette of India, Extra, Pt. II, Sec. 4, dated 12th September, 2008.
